@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### GET /openapi.json — generated OpenAPI 3.1 spec
GET {{baseUrl}}/openapi.json

###

### GET /docs — Scalar UI (open in browser)
GET {{baseUrl}}/docs

###

### GET /posts/:id — get a post by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts/1

###

### GET /posts/:id — invalid id (expects 400 from schema validation)
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts/abc

###

### POST /posts — create a post
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Hello Darto",
  "tags": ["dart", "backend"]
}

###

### POST /posts — missing required field (expects 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tags": ["dart"]
}
